Title: Lifecycle
Plot: The girls attend the Subaru Pink Ride to support breast cancer research. Tina is furious for Niki blowing her cover with Jenny but Adele assures her the two won't be seen together publicly. Meeting old friends prompts Tasha to ponder her long-term plans in life. A campfire game of "I never" turns into a discussion on cheating -- with devastating results.
GuestStars: Clementine Ford (Molly Kroll), Jon Wolfe Nelson (Tom)
